d generates 97% fewer vehicle emissions.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This drone delivery service\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1896}, {\"ngram\": \"ground delivery\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 1939}, {\"ngram\": \"97% fewer vehicle emissions\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hexcelis a leading carbon fiber manufacturer with a large campus in West Valley City.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Valley_City,_Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999994665814, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"West Valley City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Valley_City,_Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Valley_City,_Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hexcelis\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"a leading carbon fiber manufacturer\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"a large campus\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The company employs hundreds of Utah researchers and technicians building high-performance carbon fiber material used in the manufacturing of dozens of different air taxis,including Archer Aviation's Midnight.\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999996334736, \"rank\": 3.6647963039020546e-10, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}, {\"begin\": 2252, \"end\": 2267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archer_Aviation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Archer Aviation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archer_Aviation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Archer_Aviation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The company\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"hundreds\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2098}, {\"ngram\": \"technicians\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"high-performance carbon fiber material\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"the manufacturing\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"dozens\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2218}, {\"ngram\": \"different air taxis\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Highways in the sky will be part of Utah's air mobility ecosystem and represent the next chapter in transportation that will revolutionize the way we get around.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2317, \"end\": 2321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999996334736, \"rank\": 3.6647963039020546e-10, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Highways\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"the next chapter\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2377}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imagine a world in which life-saving medication, or even doctors, are delivered directly to your door.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2545, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"even doctors\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2507}, {\"ngram\": \"your door\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Or imagine traveling from your home to the Salt Lake International Airport in less than ten minutes.\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2589, \"end\": 2620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City_International_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Salt Lake International Airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City_International_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City_International_Airport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your home\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"less than ten minutes\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Utahns will benefit greatly from reduced traffic congestion, giving them more time to spend with family and friends; enhanced access to jobs and educational opportunities; and significantly improved air quality.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Utahns\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"reduced traffic congestion\", \"from\": 2681, \"to\": 2707}, {\"ngram\": \"more time\", \"from\": 2721, \"to\": 2730}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 2756, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"enhanced access\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2780}, {\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"educational opportunities\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2818}, {\"ngram\": \"air quality\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More transportation choices that include air mobility will directly support this freedom of movement.\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More transportation choices\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2887}, {\"ngram\": \"air mobility\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2913}, {\"ngram\": \"this freedom\", \"from\": 2936, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"movement\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Utah legislators have enacted forward-thinking policies to create a regulatory framework in which advanced air mobility technologies can flourish.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999996334736, \"rank\": 3.6647963039020546e-10, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"forward-thinking policies\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"a regulatory framework\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"advanced air mobility technologies\", \"from\": 3061, \"to\": 3095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have passed laws enabling the creation of air mobility corridors and directed the Utah Department of Transportation to create an advanced air mobility sandbox that will accelerate these technologies in a safe testing environment.\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"laws\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"the creation\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"air mobility corridors\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"the Utah Department\", \"from\": 3193, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"Transportation\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"an advanced air mobility sandbox\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3273}, {\"ngram\": \"these technologies\", \"from\": 3295, \"to\": 3313}, {\"ngram\": \"a safe testing environment\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Utah is uniquely positioned to lead the world in establishing highways in the sky by the 2034 Winter Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3346, \"end\": 3350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999996334736, \"rank\": 3.6647963039020546e-10, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"highways\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3416}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3427}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2034 Winter Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By integrating advanced air mobility solutions into our infrastructure, we will not only enhance Utahns' connectivity and mobility but also create a more sustainable future.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"advanced air mobility solutions\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3508}, {\"ngram\": \"our infrastructure\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"Utahns' connectivity\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3579}, {\"ngram\": \"mobility\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3592}, {\"ngram\": \"a more sustainable future\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3634}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Realizing this vision, however, requires decisive action.\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this vision\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"decisive action\", \"from\": 3677, \"to\": 3692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Utah must invest in research and development, foster public-private partnerships and continue to enact policies that support advanced air mobility innovation and deployment.\", \"from\": 3694, \"to\": 3867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3694, \"end\": 3698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999996334736, \"rank\": 3.6647963039020546e-10, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"development\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3738}, {\"ngram\": \"foster public-private partnerships\", \"from\": 3740, \"to\": 3774}, {\"ngram\": \"policies\", \"from\": 3797, \"to\": 3805}, {\"ngram\": \"advanced air mobility innovation\", \"from\": 3819, \"to\": 3851}, {\"ngram\": \"deployment\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The state has a unique opportunity to showcase its continued commitment to an unmatched quality of life.\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The state\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3878}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique opportunity\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3903}, {\"ngram\": \"its continued commitment\", \"from\": 3916, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"an unmatched quality\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3964}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3968, \"to\": 3972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Utah can lead the world in this new era of transportation.\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 4032, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3974, \"end\": 3978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999996334736, \"rank\": 3.6647963039020546e-10, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 3997}, {\"ngram\": \"this new era\", \"from\": 4001, \"to\": 4013}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We must seize the moment and create a future where the sky's no longer the limit.\", \"from\": 4033, \"to\": 4114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4057}, {\"ngram\": \"a future\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4077}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4091}, {\"ngram\": \"the limit\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aaron Starks is the president and CEO and Robert Carroll is the Chief of Staff of 47G, Utah's aerospace and defense association.\", \"from\": 4116, \"to\": 4244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4116, \"end\": 4121, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron\", \"score\": 0.997751079448105, \"rank\": 0.0011964577050704093, \"text\": \"Aaron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aaron\"}, {\"begin\": 4122, \"end\": 4128, \"